# Powershell API fun:

## Random Advice
```powershell
$r = Invoke-RestMethod "https://api.adviceslip.com/advice"; Write-Host "`nâœ¨ " -NoNewline -ForegroundColor Cyan; Write-Host "COSMIC WISDOM #$($r.slip.id)" -ForegroundColor Yellow; Write-Host ("â•" * 60) -ForegroundColor DarkGray; Write-Host "`n   :thought_balloon:  " -NoNewline -ForegroundColor Magenta; Write-Host $r.slip.advice -ForegroundColor White; Write-Host "`n" ("â•" * 60) -ForegroundColor DarkGray; Write-Host ""; Start-Sleep -Milliseconds 100; 1..30 | % { Write-Host "ðŸŒŸ" -NoNewline -ForegroundColor $(Get-Random @("Red","Yellow","Green","Cyan","Magenta")); Start-Sleep -Milliseconds 50 }; Write-Host "`n"
```

## Space Station Location and Crew
```powershell
$iss = Invoke-RestMethod "http://api.open-notify.org/iss-now.json"; $people = Invoke-RestMethod "http://api.open-notify.org/astros.json"; Write-Host "`nðŸš€ INTERNATIONAL SPACE STATION" -ForegroundColor Cyan; Write-Host "ðŸ“ Current Location:" -ForegroundColor Yellow; Write-Host "   Latitude:  $($iss.iss_position.latitude)Â°" -ForegroundColor Green; Write-Host "   Longitude: $($iss.iss_position.longitude)Â°" -ForegroundColor Green; Write-Host "`nðŸ‘¨â€ðŸš€ $($people.number) humans in space right now:" -ForegroundColor Magenta; $people.people | Group-Object craft | % { Write-Host "`nðŸ›¸ $($_.Name):" -ForegroundColor Yellow; $_.Group | % { Write-Host "   â€¢ $($_.name)" -ForegroundColor Cyan } }; Write-Host ""
```

## Dad Joke
```powershell
$j = Invoke-RestMethod "https://icanhazdadjoke.com" -Headers @{Accept="application/json"}; Write-Host "`nðŸ‘¨ " -NoNewline -ForegroundColor Yellow; Write-Host "DAD JOKE ALERT!" -ForegroundColor Red; Write-Host ("â”€" * 50) -ForegroundColor DarkGray; Write-Host "`nðŸ’­ $($j.joke)" -ForegroundColor Cyan; Write-Host "`n"; 1..5 | % { Write-Host "ðŸ˜‚" -NoNewline; Start-Sleep -Milliseconds 200 }; Write-Host " *ba dum tss*" -ForegroundColor DarkGray
```

## Cat Fact
```powershell
$cat = Invoke-RestMethod "https://catfact.ninja/fact"; Write-Host "`n  /\_/\  " -ForegroundColor Yellow; Write-Host " ( o.o ) " -ForegroundColor Yellow; Write-Host "  > ^ <  " -ForegroundColor Yellow; Write-Host "`nðŸ± CAT FACT:" -ForegroundColor Magenta; Write-Host ("â•" * ($cat.fact.Length + 4)) -ForegroundColor DarkCyan; Write-Host "  $($cat.fact)" -ForegroundColor White; Write-Host ("â•" * ($cat.fact.Length + 4)) -ForegroundColor DarkCyan
```

## Today in History
```powershell
$d = Get-Date; $h = Invoke-RestMethod "https://history.muffinlabs.com/date/$($d.Month)/$($d.Day)"; Write-Host "`nðŸ“… ON THIS DAY IN HISTORY: $($d.ToString('MMMM dd'))" -ForegroundColor Yellow -BackgroundColor DarkBlue; $h.data.Events | Select -First 3 | % { Write-Host "`n:alarm_clock: Year $($_.year):" -ForegroundColor Cyan; Write-Host "   $($_.text)" -ForegroundColor White }
```

## Your IP Location
```powershell
$ip = Invoke-RestMethod "http://ip-api.com/json/"; Write-Host "`n    ðŸŒ" -ForegroundColor Blue; Write-Host "YOUR DIGITAL FOOTPRINT" -ForegroundColor Cyan; Write-Host "â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”" -ForegroundColor DarkGray; Write-Host "ðŸ“ IP: $($ip.query)" -ForegroundColor Yellow; Write-Host "ðŸ™ï¸  $($ip.city), $($ip.regionName), $($ip.country)" -ForegroundColor Green; Write-Host "ðŸ¢ ISP: $($ip.isp)" -ForegroundColor Magenta; Write-Host "ðŸ“ Coords: $($ip.lat), $($ip.lon)" -ForegroundColor Cyan
```

# Wisdom from Yeezy
```powershell
$k = Invoke-RestMethod "https://api.kanye.rest"; Write-Host "`nðŸŽ¤ KANYE SAYS:" -ForegroundColor Magenta -BackgroundColor Black; Write-Host "`n   â$($k.quote)âž" -ForegroundColor Yellow; Write-Host "`n                              - Ye" -ForegroundColor DarkGray
```

## Bitcoin Price 
```powershell
$btc = Invoke-RestMethod "https://api.coinbase.com/v2/exchange-rates?currency=BTC"; $price = [math]::Round($btc.data.rates.USD, 2); Write-Host "`nâ‚¿ Bitcoin: `$$price USD`n" -ForegroundColor Green
```